    <section id="fs-id2241645" type="problems-exercises" class="problems-exercises"><title>Problems &amp; Exercises</title><exercise id="fs-id1745122" type="problems-exercises"><problem id="fs-id2810576"><para id="import-auto-id2750203">(a) The hot and neutral wires supplying DC power to a light-rail commuter train carry 800 A and are separated by 75.0 cm. What is the magnitude and direction of the force between 50.0 m of these wires? (b) Discuss the practical consequences of this force, if any.</para>
